Spring annotation application
Spring annotation application add @ComponentScan @Filter FilterType.CUSTOM implements TypeFilter,@Scope--》prototype,singleton,调用方法创建对象的时机
Spring annotation application add @Lazy @Bean 懒加载，不在IOC容器启动时加载，而是在第一次获取时加载，并初始化
Spring annotation application add @Conditional implements Condition Type and Method,@Import类似于@Bean，都是导入第三方包的组件，id默认是全类名
Spring annotation application add @Import implements ImportSelector 返回类的全类名，还是容器注册，implements ImportBeanDefinitionRegistrar 手动注册
Spring annotation application add @Bean implements FactoryBean ===>getObject getObjectType isSingleton &colorFactoryBean
Spring annotation application add @Bean （initMethod destoryMethod) AnnotationConfigApplicationContext(MainConfigOfLifeCycle.class)
Spring annotation application add InitializingBean DisposableBean @PostConstructor @PreDestroy implements BeanPostProcessor postProcessorBeforeInitializing postProcessorAfterInitializing
Spring annotation application add interface BeanPostProcessor对注解进行解析，@Value SPL ${} @PropertySource @Autowired @Qualifier指定 @Primary 默认优先
Spring annotation application add @Profile 加在类上 需要满足条件才会进行里面的组件注册 加在方法上 不影响其他的Bean注册 注册只是组件初始化的第一步 更确切的说 是class.newInstances()的前奏
Spring annotation application add @Aspect 切面类 @Before @After @AfterReturning @AfterThrowing @Around @Configuratio @EnableAspectJAutoProxy
Spring annotation application add AnnotationAwareAspectJAutoProxyCreator 后置处理器 @EnableTransactionalManagemnt PlatformTransactionManager事务管理器 代理对象 事务拦截器 MethodInterceptor
servlet 3.0 @WebServlet @WebListener @WebFilter
Spring mvc ServletContainerInitializer AbstractDispatcherServletAdapter Callable<String> return String DeferredResult<Object> setResult return Object
编程式事务，声明式事务（注解版，xml版） 事务的7种传播级别(required,required_new,supports,not_supports,mandatory,never,nested)
spring mvc spring ioc thread jdbc
mybatis query field.set(),res====>使用反射塞值，其他的insert,update,delete只需要执行sql即可
ExtArrayList=====》扩容 1.5倍，解决容量为一的bug，Vector扩容2倍，加了synchronized
extHashMap resize头插法 put也是头插法 node = new Node<K,V>(key,value,node);table[index] = node
Spring Cloud Eurak注册中心@EnableEurekaClient @EnableEurekaServer
Spring Cloud @EnableDiscoveryClient @EnableHystrix @FeginClients(整合了ribbon的负载均衡），Spring Cloud Config 分布式配置中心 @RefreshScope /actuator/refresh
